.claude/

# Website deploy artifacts — big binaries / regenerated per release
appcast.xml
site/public/dmg/
site/public/releases/
site/public/review-demo.mp4

# Private deployment notes & local tooling (never part of the public repo)
CLAUDE.md
.hawkfile

# Private Liftoff relay server and deployment source
relay/
